name: Recreate a waiting after voiding ticket

steps.name: Given I am on the HOME page
When I wait for the page fully loaded
And I navigate to "Check In" on the navigation bar
Then I should be redirected to WAITING_LIST page
When I click on the "Add Customer" button in the waiting page
Then I should see the text "Create Waiting" visible
When I click on the Select customer
And I click on the "CLICK HERE TO ADD CUSTOMER" button
Expect "toBeVisible" getByRole('button', { name: 'CLICK HERE TO ADD CUSTOMER', exact: true })
Click getByRole('button', { name: 'CLICK HERE TO ADD CUSTOMER', exact: true })
Then I should see a popup dialog with title "Create New Customer"
When I fill the new customer name "Recreate"
And I fill the new customer phone
And I click on the "SAVE" button in the create new customer dialog
Then I should see a new customer "Recreate" on ticket
When I select the "FULL SET & FILL IN" category
Expect "toHaveText" locator('button.MuiButtonBase-root').getByText('FULL SET & FILL IN', { exact: true })
Click locator('button.MuiButtonBase-root').getByText('FULL SET & FILL IN', { exact: true })
When I add the "Full set" service to my cart
Then I should see a popup dialog with title "Pick Technician"
When I click on the "Anna" text inside the content section of the opening dialog
Click locator('div[role="dialog"]').filter({ has: locator('#alert-dialog-title') }).locator('div.MuiDialogContent-root').getByText('Anna', { exact: true }).last()
Then I should see the service "Full set" in my cart
And I should see the duration "25 mins" in my cart
When I click on the "SAVE" button
And I wait for the page fully loaded
Then I should be redirected to WAITING_LIST page
When I wait for the page fully loaded
Then I should see the customer "Recreate" in the waiting list
And I should see the service "Full set" in the waiting list
And I should see the technician "Anna" in the waiting list
When I wait for the page fully loaded
And I click on the first row for customer "Recreate" to expand details
Then I should see the "Create Ticket" button visible
When I click on the "Create Ticket" button
Expect "toBeVisible" getByRole('button', { name: 'Create Ticket', exact: true })
Click getByRole('button', { name: 'Create Ticket', exact: true })
And I wait for the page fully loaded
Then I should see the "Ticket View" screen
And I should see the "Manicure" service
And I should see the user info "Anna" in the ticket
When I wait for the page fully loaded
And I void the current open ticket with reason "Mistake"

Expect "toBeVisible" locator('div[role="dialog"]').filter({ has: locator('#alert-dialog-title').filter({ hasText: 'SELECT VOID REASON' }) }).or(locator('div[role="dialog"]').filter({ has: locator('#alert-dialog-title').filter({ hasText: 'VOID TICKET' }) }))
Click locator('div[role="dialog"]').filter({ has: locator('#alert-dialog-title').filter({ hasText: 'SELECT VOID REASON' }) }).getByText('Mistake')
Click locator('div[role="dialog"]').filter({ has: locator('#draggable-dialog-title').filter({ hasText: 'CONFIRM VOID' }) }).getByRole('button', { name: 'CONFIRM' })
Then I should be redirected to HOME page
When I navigate to "Check In" on the navigation bar
Then I should be redirected to WAITING_LIST page
When I wait for the page fully loaded
And I click on the first row for customer "Recreate" to expand details
Then I should see the "Create Ticket" button visible
When I click on the "Create Ticket" button
Expect "toBeVisible" getByRole('button', { name: 'Create Ticket', exact: true })
Click getByRole('button', { name: 'Create Ticket', exact: true })
Then I should see the "Ticket View" screen
When I click on the "PAY" button
Then I should see the text "PAYMENT TICKET" visible
And I should see the text "PAYMENT HISTORY" visible
And I should see the button with id "payment" visible
When I click on the element with id "payment"
Then I should see a popup dialog with title "Close Ticket"
And I should see a popup dialog with content "CHANGE$0.00OK"
When I click on the "OK" button in the popup dialog
Then I should be redirected to HOME page
